Every Software project needs an isolated Environments

--> Container => Software & Hardware dependencies

Example:
    1. Project A --> Python --> Tensorflow  2.4.1  --> Environment ---> (Software modules)
        --> May get crashed
    2. Project B --> Python --> Tensorflow  2.7.1




Environment --> Collection of software modules 


Environments --> 

    1. Python Virtual Environments
    2. virtualenv --> package
    3. pip install virtualenv
    4. PATH setting for virtualenv
        1. path from pip3 install virtualenv
        2. export PATH="<path>:$PATH" --> Ubuntu, Macos, Windows --> GitBash

    5. virtualenv env --> will create an environment
    6. source env/bin/activate --> Ubuntu, MacOS, GitBash in Windows
       source env\Scripts\activate.bat --> CMD in Windows

    7. requirements.txt